日無買花西撚足我半日<br />\n之前又話買花好無謂。食返餐仲好<br />\n屌，咁咪唔撚買囉，今日又屌鳩我唔送野。<br />\n我咪好好聲同佢講「咪買左件野比你囉，唔通你寧願收花都唔要呢份禮物咩」<br />\n我當堂嬲撚到跳舞。屌！<br />\n佢話寧願收到$60既花都唔想要呢份野<br />\n<br />\nPS；份禮物係佢話想要左好耐</blockquote><br />\n打少左句。我問完之後佢話係<br />\n痴撚線"},{"pid":"f649e4bf75d6c62b86fbaec14568c90ccbcf134e","tid":120271,"uid":56912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T15:30:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一開始拍拖已經講定唔好送<br />\n其實我唔理解收到花有咩咁開心<br />\n情人節唔係通常要行街睇戲食飯架咩？<br />\n咁咪要攞住札花周圍走？<br />\n渣住咁大舊野去行街入店鋪/入戲院/入餐廳，咪好唔方便做咩都只可以單手做囉？<br />\n唔通要拎翻屋企擺低先再出去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申 拍拖3年無收過花</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n之前試過放左係公司<br />\n第二日俾啲同事話我無人性<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7bb81ba15aac9cb32f52e51f8021468a8ccf8b72","tid":120271,"uid":20950,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T15:32:59.000Z","msg":"鼻敏感收花會打乞痴打到斷氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d73b7ac93517c0a66eb416ed37e0e46726186d9b","tid":120271,"uid":24308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T15:33:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>留名睇下幾多絲打衝出嚟拎貞節牌坊</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb90e2d67b2c5f476292811474df2760252c0b95","tid":120271,"uid":30076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T15:35:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>留名睇下幾多絲打衝出嚟拎貞節牌坊</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係呀。班撚樣就係講一套做一套呀"},{"pid":"80e5c0660651a66a842daa7d5cb9d837bf146d4c","tid":120271,"uid":30076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T15:35:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>留名睇下幾多絲打衝出嚟拎貞節牌坊</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji