s/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果琴日有人送俾我就好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2aae8a4cab68b71eeee033bdd9827d8675f91339","tid":120271,"uid":84950,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T23:36:00.000Z","msg":"中意收乾花。。唔好咁大紥，太大好柒<br />\n鮮花要要顧佢倒轉會漏水又要怕佢放得耐生蟲<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n乾花起碼可以俾我做啲手作嘢"},{"pid":"024fc6c7bef87b1e61e33d8a78ea2b627d7d4f1b","tid":120271,"uid":943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T23:40:15.000Z","msg":"睇吓咩花啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我唔鐘意玫瑰啊大大朵嗰啲<br />\n我鐘意滿天星<br />\n冇話特別想收花，但收到真係會勁開心，咩花都好，我都會好開心<br />\n利申 男友今年冇送花，乜都冇送，但過得好開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0aea634470d8786cbc14108ae57a642b04b41a24","tid":120271,"uid":45016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T23:41:28.000Z","msg":"千幾蚊一紮 擺唔擺到一星期我想問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  收果下應該真係會好開心覺得好sweet既 不過事後點處理果紮野又係麻煩 有咁多錢去食餐好野算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n琴日碌IG FB 全部都係條女捧住紮花坐係高級餐廳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而我男朋友係送左戒指   糖 比我既<br />\n2蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f3509120c2955fe9357d8462103b7cf402